# Todo App

A full-featured Todo App built with [React], allowing users to manage their tasks efficiently. This application includes user authentication, profile management, and comprehensive todo management features.

## Features

- **User Authentication**: 
  - Register and log in to your account
  - Password reset functionality

- **Profile Management**:
  - Edit user profile information
  - Change password

- **Todo Management**:
  - Add new todos
  - Edit existing todos
  - Mark todos as done
  - Delete todos

## Technologies Used

- **Frontend**: [React]
- **Backend**: [Node.js,Express]
- **Database**: [MongoDB]
- **Authentication**: [JWT]
- **Styling**: [CSS]


